{
  "title": "Tangy Spicy Ethiopian Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A spicy and flavorful one-pot Ethiopian dish featuring green chilli and lacquer-glaze, low in fat and rich in flavor. This stew is perfect for a cold winter night.",
